explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the association between medication for opioid use disorder (MOUD) treatment and healthcare costs among Medicaid beneficiaries. It does not mention any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models, nor does it involve any of the listed keywords related to machine learning, deep learning, or large language models.
